\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Luk 22:31; 1 Tesalonika 5:6; Akar Mogomem 12:12\x*Ia angamÉØra ikÉØ, uari bagh gan. Satan, gumazir ian apanimÉØn itir kam, a laionÉØn mÉØn tiarim akara diagharui. A zurara gumazamizibar amasa me buriagharui.
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Aposel 14:22; Efesus 6:11-13; 2 Timoti 3:12; Jems 4:7\x*Ia fo, GodÉØn gumazamizir nguazir kamÉØn itiba, me uaghan mÉØzazir ia isir kaba isi. KamaghÉØn amizÉØ ia bar nÉØghnÉØzir gavgavimÉØn tugh gavgavigh Satan batogh.
